{"tid":1740642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搞清楚，被捕同被羈留人士都係有權投票嘅","createTime":"2019-11-20T04:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T04:17:57.000Z","uid":65894,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b86b3286a1f986693227dff94937e82a5e225c88","tid":1740642,"uid":65894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:08:57.000Z","msg":"呢見日見到有啲手足都擔心如果區選前被狗咬的話，會因為被捕而無得投票。於是我走去睇返啲資料，發現<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">被捕人士同被羈留人士都係有權投嘅！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n睇返2008年嘅新聞，當時梁國雄就住囚犯及羈留者嘅投票權進行司法覆核勝訴，當時法官話：<br />\n//<span style=\"color: red;\">投票權毫無疑問是重要的政治權利，限制投票等同將囚犯定形，對他們造成不合理的歧視，違反《基本法》第二十六條及《人權法》第二十一條。又指出《立法會條例》只列明服刑囚犯喪失投票權，現時沒有法例限制羈留人士的投票權。</span>//<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/775083/%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F775083%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=a70a1427\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F775083%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1&h=2b140d40\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/775083/%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1</a><br />\n<br />\n所以只要你上返區選嗰網站，你係可以搵到被捕同羈留人士嘅專用票站：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQbFR4P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQbFR4P.png&h=a5e92eba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/chi/p_cs.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Fdc2019%2Fchi%2Fp_cs.html&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=f647a420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/chi/p_cs.html</a><br />\n<br />\n總結，我唔係叫大家放心出去發夢。不過投票的確係香港人嘅權利，包括被捕同被羈留人士，如果你真係唔好彩被狗咬，記得要清楚自己接有嘅權利，向啲狗提出安排你去投票。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n香港人加油！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e9c609e53b06e0a9fa462ddd42bed3e0f982c3eb","tid":1740642,"uid":26993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:11:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"085adda3802c947cc58fe31a9c276341a65dae8e","tid":1740642,"uid":279925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:13:57.000Z","msg":"已經過左堂交比懲教署看管就投到。。係臭格扣留的話係有權投，但pk狗會話冇人手帶你去投"},{"pid":"e63174460705983b0605e63b8cf5da466c46417b","tid":1740642,"uid":279925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:15:50.000Z","msg":"情況同你係臭格話睇醫生一樣。。朝早叫睇醫生可能夜晚先帶你去！！投票呢d你覺得佢會好合作咁帶你去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26d0aadeb89ad49e4097f62ff1443ad26a5afb4","tid":1740642,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:16:00.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"e3ed0ebdf37a8af9131fb5e12d8736a0e1979e48","tid":1740642,"uid":282979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec89f69c5389e7dda2af05a12423b03c75959c7","tid":1740642,"uid":65894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e63174460705983b0605e63b8cf5da466c46417b","tid":1740642,"uid":279925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:15:50.000Z","msg":"情況同你係臭格話睇醫生一樣。。朝早叫睇醫生可能夜晚先帶你去！！投票呢d你覺得佢會好合作咁帶你去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:17:57.000Z","msg":"預咗啲狗一定用程序嚟撚啲手足，但唔想佢哋連自己有權投票都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}